name: Jeremy Lin-Sanity New York Knickerbocker Frazzle Towel
description:
This Limited Edition Frazzle Towel is part of the Lin-Sanity bandwagon in New York City. If you don't know the story, you better ask somebody...

The Frazzle Towel features the basketball in a straight jacket. When the new 2K basketball game drops, wave your Lin-Sanity Frazzle Towel in your opponents grill as you take him/her to the rack, drop dimes to Melo, or rain 3s in their mouf.
OR
Take it to the games next year to support the homie, Jeremy Lin. 

UPDATE: The Lin-sanity Frazzle Towel is currently sold out but you may back order and receive in 2 weeks or less.

name: ILL StICK
